name: Mayakashi Winter
desc: Monsters your opponent controls lose 100 ATK/DEF for each “Mayakashi” monster in your GY with a different name. You can send this card and 1 face-up “Mayakashi” monster you control to the GY; draw 1 card. You can banish this card and 1 Zombie monster from your GY, then target 1 “Mayakashi” monster in your GY; Special Summon it. You can only use 1 “Mayakashi Winter” effect per turn, and only once that turn.
